description:
My place is close to Apollo, Columbia University, The 1,2,3, A,B,C,D Train Lines, Slyvia's, Harlem Night's, Starbucks, The Grange Bar & Eatery, Picante, Café One, Trufa,. You’ll love my place because of the high ceilings, the kitchen, the location, and the coziness. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers.

Guests cannot access or use the washing machine or dryer.
name: NYC Harlem Studio w/ 2 beds, Close to Trains
review: Great place gives you the authentic city fell accessible to everything great food within walking distance enjoyed my stay.
